HEADWORD: Spellwork
<hw>Spell"work`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Power or effect of
magic; that which is wrought by magic; enchantment.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Like those Peri isles of light⟦br⟧
That hang by <qex>spellwork</qex> in the air.</q>
<rj><qau>Moore.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

